{"tid":1699474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［兄弟爬山各自努力]請各位抗爭者忠於自己，亦唔需要挑戰他人理念。","createTime":"2019-11-08T04:51:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T05:46:11.000Z","uid":195995,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f8fa8e24ac4e84327b88e27a645c59dfe309eb2b","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:51:36.000Z","msg":"由而家呢刻開始，各位抗爭者想開花既就開花，想燒衣既就燒衣，想和理非就和理非。請對自己既理念負上責任，而唔需要憂慮其他人既諗法或風向。<br />\n<br />\n因為所有風向及意見都未必適合每個人，並非每一句「你冷靜d先」都出現在應該冷靜既時候；並非每一句「仲等幾時」都出現在應該立即行動既時候。或者每一刻都適合，或者每一刻都唔適合，請自己去判斷，行動及承擔，唔需要別人為你負責。<br />\n<br />\n最重要既係，在忠於自己既同時，唔好挑戰其他人既諗法。大家都生活在知識水平高既地方，都好有自己想法，但係我地畢竟唔係軍師，冇咁既料，亦冇咁既需要。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">既使你既意見再正確都好，請相信別人做決定前已經做好佢地覺悟，佢做好覺悟，錯了，冇人會怪你見死不救。</span></strong></span>再挑戰別人既想法，係打壓緊呢一場抗爭既有志之士，亦係打壓緊呢場運動既進程。<br />\n<br />\n或者諗下基本上冇所謂既正唔正確，岳義士救人好正確；佢都可以停低諗一諗，咁佢而家可能無官司係身，都可以好正確。<br />\n<br />\n所以請不要說：「你覺得咁做可以改變到乜野？」<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">試著說：「請應承我地，你一定要平安而歸！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭經已去到樽頸位，但我深信，我地各位一定能夠成功突破呢個樽頸位。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">應承我，你地一定要平安而歸。</span></span>"},{"pid":"55ca58ef375c39f2779b2b5e2c05afb3ca65bea4","tid":1699474,"uid":89963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T04:56:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cf2c3807f491d7ba980cd55208e83278d56f4a0","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:14:41.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"7fdbbd7fe41c59efd47df01e5fac4ccd3215304f","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:14:51.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"82537176c7115d1ebfec284642799fcc1112303b","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:15:20.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"62dbf2603ff46163c3b4ee959b74fecb8c5a8f24","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:15:46.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"8abcb2dc0287500457f194176a224d9e856214e7","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:16:10.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"9efeb692a3168be2a8a8e95753a52d3ad383d1cc","tid":1699474,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0472e615518593c52c68deadb5c1a33316b2e336","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:16:50.000Z","msg":"應承我，你地一定要平安而歸。5/10"},{"pid":"8b7a08db56b208743fa6449e22d16b2efca19822","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:17:37.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"201042826ae43581e81bd04e3dfaa53999deba74","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"4ef469042f1f2958e20c30b688c4d42cb9187a0b","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:18:32.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"be63ee1f0e62c7ce33ae7212b612932c2143ebc6","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:18:44.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"7f0d0651d3c6d18d3c6546b3096dd274da9fbaa2","tid":1699474,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:18:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b332b80c3b4c3e350112c4b159e3b38cca1ffb45","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:18:58.000Z","msg":"應承我，你地一定要平安而歸。10/10"},{"pid":"32182d9fbf0723f7f81ed0bc67672e925d04904b","tid":1699474,"uid":195995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T05:21:43.000Z","msg":"應承我，你地一定要平安而歸。"},{"pid":"32b3267d2d51a6630f91ac5fa1d9fdf8205c46a6","tid":1699474,"uid":29555,"like":1,"dislik